9:
Hey, wait! You're those foxes from 
earlier!
16:
But so long as life remains in my body, 
I WILL defend this place!
25:
Awa, Mugi, Hie—stand back!
Fear not, for Inaho Tamamo is here!
26:
Those mortals will NEVER know what hit
—
39:
The kits and I put our lives on the line 
to buy you time to escape! Why are 
you still here?!
47:
Nonsense! You are a princess! I simply 
CANNOT allow you to stand on the 
front lines!
51:
Princess-shmincess! I would never 
leave you behind! How could I?!
58:
Oh, what is it now?!
Can't you see I'm busy at the 
moment?!
60:
Look, we're uh...
We aren't here to fight you guys, okay? 
We just wanted to talk.
63:
We would like to know why you're 
haunting Soushiro.
66:
Haunting?
Oh, OH goodness. Is THAT what all this 
fuss is about?
68:
You see, Princess Inaho has taken 
quite the fancy to him. Why, she's 
absolutely—
74:
AAAH!
LA LA LAAA, I CANNOT HEEEAR YOU!
79:
Oh, please.
Seems like the "hauntings" were all just 
a kid with a big fat crush on the local 
pretty boy.
84:
Nimbus, have you ever heard of this 
cool thing called "delicacy?"
87:
What's the point of beating around the 
bush? She's obviously got a thing for 
him.
98:
She has something to give him? Is that 
why she keeps visiting?
101:
Oh boy... See, Inaho here likes 
Soushiro. Y'know, in a romantic way?
105: I-in a romantic way? I see...
109:
Priiincess and Soooushiro, sitting in 
a tree!
K! I! S!—
113:
Hush, now. Honestly, I'm at my wits' 
end. He always dodges the subject—
and we can't restrain him long enough 
for her to confess!
116:
It's been DAYS upon days, and the silly 
girl's made no progress! None at all!
120: You don't mind that he's human?
122:
I most certainly DO! Not only is it 
HIGHLY irresponsible, I can't imagine 
anything good will come of it—if 
anything comes of it at all!
132:
YOU WOULD NEVER UNDERSTAND! Say 
what you like—I will NEVER give up!
136:
I LOVE SOUSHIRO! And what of it? 
I swear to you, one day Soushiro WILL 
be mine!
140:
OH! Oh no... Oh NO!
NO, NO, NOOOOO!
